        "collapsible_tab_6Xnp4d": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What hair types are Pyrosso products best for?",
            "content": "<p>Pyrosso products are designed to work across most hair types, with a focus on straight to wavy hair and thick to medium textures. Our formulas are especially effective for adding texture, control, and natural hold without stiffness.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WLVH7X": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will Pyrosso products make my hair look greasy or heavy?",
            "content": "<p>No. Pyrosso products are formulated to provide hold and texture while keeping a clean, lightweight finish. They’re designed to add definition without weighing your hair down or leaving residue.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_brc7hr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How strong is the hold?",
            "content": "<p>Pyrosso offers a workable, long-lasting hold that keeps your style in place while still allowing movement. You can restyle throughout the day without your hair feeling stiff or crunchy.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_4TVPPe": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use Pyrosso products on dry hair?",
            "content": "<p>Yes. Pyrosso products work best on dry or slightly damp hair. Applying to dry hair gives you more texture and control, while damp hair offers a softer, more natural finish.</p>",
